00:04:39.810 --> 00:04:42.450
R-Right...

00:04:45.550 --> 00:04:47.940
Y-Yes, just like that.

00:04:57.150 --> 00:04:59.130
Wh-What's wrong, Avdol?

00:04:59.130 --> 00:05:02.910
