00:05:02.910 --> 00:05:06.080
Doesn't this look very risqué?

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:08.550
If anyone saw us, they might get the wrong idea...

00:05:08.550 --> 00:05:11.920
N-No one's looking! Hurry up and slide free!

00:05:14.390 --> 00:05:17.340
They brought even more friends!

00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:21.600
H-Hey! Go away! Stop looking at us!

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:24.950
Hey! I said go away, you damn brats!

00:05:24.950 --> 00:05:27.660
Avdol, hurry! Hurry up and slide off!

00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:29.750
That's easier said than done...

00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:35.430
This is not the role I've taken! I swear it isn't!

00:05:35.430 --> 00:05:37.290
Fine, then I'll move!

00:05:37.290 --> 00:05:40.000
M-Mr. Joestar, slow down!

00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:53.300
Stick

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:58.170
Mr. Joestar, if you move like that...

00:06:01.470 --> 00:06:04.260
I-It's the old lady from the hotel!

00:06:04.670 --> 00:06:07.760
I thought you were a wonderful gentleman,

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:10.480
but to think you're into this sort of filth!

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:13.110
How dare you play with a woman's heart?!

00:06:13.110 --> 00:06:15.190
You cheater!

00:06:15.190 --> 00:06:20.610
Hurry! Hurry, Avdol! I'm starting to cry!

00:06:20.610 --> 00:06:22.910
You villain!

00:06:25.030 --> 00:06:27.910
Help me! Oh my God!

00:06:27.910 --> 00:06:30.000
Wait... This is a misunderstanding!

00:06:34.850 --> 00:06:36.260
We did it!

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:40.380
We need to stay apart, Avdol!

00:06:40.380 --> 00:06:43.280
Your magnetism is growing stronger and stronger.

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:47.390
Curse you, damned fool! Go to hell!

00:06:54.820 --> 00:06:56.980
There she is. It's that woman.

00:06:56.980 --> 00:07:00.080
She's got some nerve,
just sitting there and smoking.

00:07:00.490 --> 00:07:02.750
Avdol, approach her from that side.

00:07:02.750 --> 00:07:05.240
Don't let her get away this time.

00:07:05.630 --> 00:07:08.120
She seems like a strong woman.

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:10.740
She may have laid a trap for us.

00:07:12.980 --> 00:07:15.360
N-No, Mr. Joestar...

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:18.300
It seems we've already fallen into her trap!

00:07:22.450 --> 00:07:24.210
Bam

00:07:22.540 --> 00:07:24.250
A railroad track!

00:07:24.250 --> 00:07:27.060
M-My foot is stuck!

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:36.610
A-Again...

00:07:36.610 --> 00:07:37.690
