00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:40.820
...stuck together!

00:07:45.110 --> 00:07:46.460
Son of a bi—

00:07:56.710 --> 00:07:58.750
What is it, Mr. Joestar?

00:08:00.130 --> 00:08:04.660
