00:11:20.370 --> 00:11:21.670
Boom

00:11:22.960 --> 00:11:29.090
What are you imagining?
My chest didn't get bigger...

00:11:32.910 --> 00:11:37.350
Your magnetism just got stronger.

00:11:37.350 --> 00:11:39.770
