00:16:11.040 --> 00:16:14.770
Now, at the last moment, the tables have turned!

00:16:29.570 --> 00:16:32.080
A pincer attack?

00:16:32.080 --> 00:16:34.520
You still don't get it.

00:16:35.060 --> 00:16:39.940
You think you've cornered me,
but it's you two who are cornered.

00:16:39.940 --> 00:16:41.640
Look above you!

00:16:45.900 --> 00:16:47.620
High voltage power lines!

00:16:47.620 --> 00:16:49.540
Crap! Power lines are...

00:16:50.690 --> 00:16:53.910
That's right. Power lines are magnetic.

00:16:58.920 --> 00:17:01.550
You'll burn to a crisp!

00:17:03.120 --> 00:17:05.490
Magician's Red!

00:17:07.430 --> 00:17:09.680
Hermit Purple!

00:17:11.860 --> 00:17:15.260
Avdol can defend himself
with his flames, just barely,

00:17:15.260 --> 00:17:18.240
but you have no chance, Joestar.

00:17:18.240 --> 00:17:23.780
My Bast's power is far greater

00:17:25.530 --> 00:17:28.340
than your Hermit Purple's!

00:17:37.920 --> 00:17:41.170
